Introduction

Suzu (Korean: 스즈, Japanese: すず) is a Japanese singer under LAPONE Entertainment. In 2023, she participated in the survival show "Produce 101 Japan: The Girls" where she ended up ranking 5th place, securing her spot as a member of the Japanese project girl group ME:I.
